        "timestamp": "2018-10-18 15:13:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n@Borislav, Currently the way we did this for the other containers is have a side car container to specify the path to /var/log/onap and let the main container specify the same location and both those containers use the same volume. For the job, if I change it, it might have unintended consequences and we mainly want to enable to this to get more information out of the logs in the host since job pod dies once its done. We are having trouble identifying the intermittent issue so having this would help with understanding what the problem could have been.",
        "patchset_number": 2
